{"tid":1192042,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國瑜花蓮造勢 主辦單位宣布現場超過10萬人","createTime":"2019-06-08T08:32:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T10:01:45.000Z","uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"81b0822d1c15cc8ad5187da0d4d28ab56440967c","tid":1192042,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T08:32:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2019/06/08/realtime/6405990.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2019%2F06%2F08%2Frealtime%2F6405990.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26exp%3D3600&h=30173f51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2019/06/08/realtime/6405991.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2019%2F06%2F08%2Frealtime%2F6405991.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26exp%3D3600&h=ff892899&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2019/06/08/realtime/6405992.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2019%2F06%2F08%2Frealtime%2F6405992.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26exp%3D3600&h=745a1680&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/apMVVMZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FapMVVMZ.png&h=e2f3f235&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X7Pknr0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX7Pknr0.png&h=9d434587&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xp7BFdG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxp7BFdG.png&h=14077e2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n16：25<br />\n韓國瑜花蓮造勢大會今天下午2點45分於花蓮市六期重畫區開始，韓國瑜預計傍晚5點進場。主辦單位稍早宣布現場已突破10萬人，稍後花蓮縣長徐榛蔚將登台助講。<br />\n<br />\n15：47<br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜花蓮造勢大會將在下午2時45分於花蓮市六期重畫區開始，韓國瑜預計傍晚5時進入會場。目前挺韓四大天王在台上致詞，主辦單位宣布，現場已經突破8萬人。<br />\n<br />\n現場主持人有台北市議員戴錫欽、王欣儀、應曉薇及花蓮縣吉安鄉長游淑貞，主辦單位提醒民眾不要與親友走散，並持續播送主題曲「我的未來不是夢」，支持民眾幾乎人手一支國旗，衣服上貼上「非韓不投」、「韓家軍」貼紙。<br />\n<br />\n現場大國旗已經攤開在會場傳接，氣氛熱烈，並有樂團及原住民舞蹈表演，並有台南市議員謝龍介助講。"},{"pid":"5cd9ac6517a7c3d4077aad34e405c6606784c167","tid":1192042,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T09:47:33.000Z","msg":"主辦單位也在5點17分，宣布現場已突破15萬人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67013a216f67d79c8047078b519c77ced80333c7","tid":1192042,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T09:57:09.000Z","msg":"目測起碼50萬人"},{"pid":"afe91d26ea85a81e346bb85d1f6d83a0deb35c6b","tid":1192042,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T09:57:40.000Z","msg":"咁64起碼100萬人"},{"pid":"798de2ff0ce4c2e666a37165ac45eec57e902db8","tid":1192042,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T09:59:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>賣台發大財！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"f764f39973cd72ab8365b189f9d37c2fb5874c82","tid":1192042,"uid":22736,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T10:01:45.000Z","msg":"咁都十萬6.4果晚咪有百三萬人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}